question: ETH above $1,800 on May 17?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if the Binance 1 minute candle for ETH/USDT titled 2023/05/17 12:00 in the ET timezone (referring to noon ET) has a final “Close” price of 1,800.01 or higher, or to "No" otherwise.

The resolution source for this market is https://www.binance.com, specifically the ETH/USDT “Close” prices, currently available at https://www.binance.com/en/trade/ETH_USDT. The Binance API url for ETH/USDT may be used in the event that the chart is unavailable.

Please note that this market is about the price according to Binance ETH/USDT, not according to other sources or spot markets.

question: Will the Dallas Stars be the 2023 NHL Champion?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if the Dallas Stars become the 2023 Stanley Cup Champion. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If it is determined at any point that it is impossible for the Dallas Stars to be the 2023 Stanley Cup Champion based on the rules of the NHL (e.g. they're eliminated in the playoffs), this market will immediately resolve to "No."

If this team is still in contention to become the champion and the champion still isn't determined by November 3, 2023, 11:59:59 PM ET, this market will resolve 50-50.

events.title: NHL Champion
events.description: This is a market group over who will win the NHL Stanley Cup in 2023.

question: Will Coinbase list $PEPE by May 31?
